Description

The Bacula Agent Deploy Server front-end(web) - BADS is a simple web server writed on GOlang for managing and deploy Bacula backup agent (bacula-client and configuration files) on host.
This web solution use ansible playbook for installation bacula agent in hosts.

Instalation

# Deploy Bacula Agent Deploy Server to PROD
cd /opt
git clone https://github.com/MykolaPerehinets/bads.git
cd /opt/bads
Verify configuration in /opt/bads/templates/todo.html
./install.sh

# Update Bacula Agent Deploy Server to PROD
cd /opt/bads
git pull https://github.com/MykolaPerehinets/bads.git
Verify configuration in /opt/bads/templates/todo.html
./install.sh

# Rsync Bacula Agent Deploy Server to PROD
rsync -uvroghtpaz --rsync-path="ionice -c 3 nice -n 12 rsync" --progress --stats "/home/mperehin/LOG_FOR WORK/bads" root@ibacula.localhost.localdomain:/opt/

Information and Usage

default username: admin
default password: admin

BADS is a Open-source projects
This folder contains a collection of Go programs and libraries
cd /opt/bads
./bads.go

